PlayLast.fm
===========

PlayLast.fm is a rhythmbox plugin to create playlist from Last.fm scrobbles.

INSTALL
-------

place a copy of the root directory (the one containing the .plugin and .py files) in .local/share/rhythmbox/plugins. See the rhythmbox documentation for more information in case of trouble.

REQUIREMENTS
------------

This plugin works with rhythmbox 2.95. It probably won't with previous version.

